com.mvp4g.client.presenter
Interface PresenterInterface<V,E extends EventBus>

Type Parameters:
V - Type of the view injected into the presenter
E - Type of the event bus used by the presenter.
All Superinterfaces:
EventHandlerInterface<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasePresenter, LazyPresenter, LazyXmlPresenter, XmlPresenter
public interface PresenterInterface<V,E extends EventBus>
extends EventHandlerInterface<E>

Interface that defines a presenter.

This interface provides getter and setter for a view and an event bus.

It is recommended to use directly BasePresenter.
